Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:57.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}終わらないメロディーを歌いだしました
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:05.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}とても大好きで　少し切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}でも　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:13.24,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}止まることができなくて嫌いになりました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:22.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}たとえ大切な君のそばでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:27.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:32.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}見える景色は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:38.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}同じにはできないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:50.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}心も　未来も　笑顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:57.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そう　まだ見ぬ愛も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:00.87,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:04.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:08.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You know what you wanna be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:10.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}わかってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.69,0:23:14.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I can believe you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:18.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You see what I want tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:28.52,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}永遠と 儚さと 震える夜もあるけれど
