Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:05.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}实在过于喜欢 同时伴随些许痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:13.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}由于无法停止已经开始厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:22.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便在重要的你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:32.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}收入眼底的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:38.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可能尽然相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:50.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论心意 未来还是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:57.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}对 还有素未谋面的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:10.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:28.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}虽然会有永恒和如烟以及孤单的夜晚
